# hmpsn.studio — Windsurf Rules

> **CLAUDE.md is the single source of truth** for all AI agent rules in this project.
> Read `CLAUDE.md` at the repo root before making any changes.

This file exists only for Windsurf/Cascade discovery. All project conventions,
design system laws, session protocol, commands, code patterns, and quality gates
are maintained in `CLAUDE.md` to avoid drift between agent config files.

## Quick Reference

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `npm run dev:all` | Frontend + backend concurrently |
| `npm run typecheck` | Type-check (uses `tsc -b --noEmit`) |
| `npx vite build` | Production build |
| `npx vitest run` | Full test suite |
| `npx tsx scripts/pr-check.ts` | Automated pre-PR checks |

